cture\"><span title=\"Network Access &amp; Infrastructure\" class=\"linkLabel_WmDU\">Network Access &amp; Infrastructure</span></a></li></ul></nav></div></div></aside><main class=\"docMainContainer_TBSr\"><div class=\"container padding-top--md padding-bottom--lg\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col docItemCol_VOVn\"><div class=\"docItemContainer_Djhp\"><article><nav class=\"theme-doc-breadcrumbs breadcrumbsContainer_Z_bl\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumbs\"><ul class=\"breadcrumbs\"><li class=\"breadcrumbs__item\"><a aria-label=\"Home page\" class=\"breadcrumbs__link\" href=\"/\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"breadcrumbHomeIcon_YNFT\"><path d=\"M10 19v-5h4v5c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-7h1.7c.46 0 .68-.57.33-.87L12.67 3.6c-.38-.34-.96-.34-1.34 0l-8.36 7.53c-.34.3-.13.87.33.87H5v7c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></a></li><li class=\"breadcrumbs__item breadcrumbs__item--active\"><span class=\"breadcrumbs__link\">Integration Documentation</span></li></ul></nav><div class=\"tocCollapsible_ETCw theme-doc-toc-mobile tocMobile_ITEo\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"clean-btn tocCollapsibleButton_TO0P\">On this page</button></div><div class=\"theme-doc-markdown markdown\"><header><h1>Integration Documentation</h1></header><p>This space exists to help partners and vendors integrate with Rigetti Quantum Cloud Services (QCS) not specifically for their own use but to offer access to others.</p>\n<p>For documentation on using QCS to run quantum programs, refer to the <a class=\"\" href=\"/\">QCS Documentation</a>.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq\" id=\"overview\">Overview<a href=\"#overview\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Overview\" title=\"Direct link to Overview\" translate=\"no\">\u200b</a></h2>\n<p>Our mutual goal in any collaboration is a positive, performant user experience for your platform's end users on Rigetti QCS.</p>\n<p>There are three key parts in integration:</p>\n<ol>\n<li class=\"\">Business Agreement: The contracts and communication which define our collaboration. This is out of scope for this technically-focused integration guide, even as they shape each integration.</li>\n<li class=\"\">Network Access &amp; Infrastructure: Connecting your systems to ours in a secure, performant, and reliable way.</li>\n<li class=\"\">User Environment: Deciding how and when your users build programs for execution on QCS, and how they submit them. This includes authenticating and authorizing your systems and users for access to QCS.</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq\" id=\"terminology\">Terminology<a href=\"#terminology\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Terminology\" title=\"Direct link to Terminology\" translate=\"no\">\u200b</a></h2>\n<p>Throughout this guide, the terms You or The Partner refers to the organization integrating with Rigetti QCS. Your Platform refers to the suite of software offered by that organization to its users.</p>\n<h2 class=\"anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq\" id=\"common-models\">Common Models<a href=\"#common-models\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Common Models\" title=\"Direct link to Common Models\" translate=\"no\">\u200b</a></h2>\n<p>While each integration is unique, the following models can serve as illustrative templates.</p>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq\" id=\"vendor-model\">Vendor Model<a href=\"#vendor-model\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Vendor Model\" title=\"Direct link to Vendor Model\" translate=\"no\">\u200b</a></h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Vendor Model\" width=\"1536\" height=\"948\" class=\"img_ev3q\" src=\"/assets/images/vendor-model-2f0c50cbf48c45bc315fa9a461b2f24a.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">In this model, the Partner maintains its own user account management and API for system access.</li>\n<li class=\"\">Users interact only with the Vendor's system directly; the vendor then collects and forwards programs from their systems to QCS, and likewise collects and returns results to their users.</li>\n<li class=\"\">Users may build and submit programs in a format native to QCS (such as Quil), or in a format specified by the Vendor and converted by the Vendor for use on QCS (such as QASM).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq\" id=\"direct-user-access-model\">Direct User Access Model<a href=\"#direct-user-access-model\" class=\"hash-link\" aria-label=\"Direct link to Direct User Access Model\" title=\"Direct link to Direct User Access Model\" translate=\"no\">\u200b</a></h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Direct User Access Model\" width=\"1536\" height=\"953\" class=\"img_ev3q\" src=\"/assets/images/direct-user-access-model-022836b3854944b9c6462f298585492a.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\">In this partnership, the Partner vets users and forwards requests for accounts with direct access to QCS.</li>\n<li class=\"\">These users then maintain QCS accounts of their own, to include account balances.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Continue to <a class=\"\" href=\"/integration/network-access-and-infrastructure\">Network Access &amp; Infrastructure</a>.</p></div></article><nav class=\"docusaurus-mt-lg pagination-nav\" aria-label=\"Docs pages\"><a class=\"pagination-nav__link pagination-nav__link--next\" href=\"/integration/language-and-client-tooling\"><div class=\"pagination-nav__sublabel\">Next</div><div class=\"pagination-nav__label\">Language and Client Tooling</div></a></nav></div></div><div class=\"col col--3\"><div class=\"tableOfContents_bqdL thin-scrollbar theme-doc-toc-desktop\"><ul class=\"table-of-contents table-of-contents__left-border\"><li><a href=\"#overview\" class=\"table-of-contents__link toc-highlight\">Overview</a></li><li><a href=\"#terminology\" class=\"table-of-contents__link toc-highlight\">Terminology</a></li><li><a href=\"#common-models\" class=\"table-of-contents__link toc-highlight\">Common Models</a><ul><li><a href=\"#vendor-model\" class=\"table-of-contents__link toc-highlight\">Vendor Model</a></li><li><a href=\"#direct-user-access-model\" class=\"table-of-contents__link toc-highlight\">Direct User Access Model</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div></div></main></div></div></div><footer class=\"theme-layout-footer footer\"><div class=\"container container-fluid\"><div class=\"footer__bottom text--center\"><div class=\"footer__copyright\">Copyright \u00a9 2026 Rigetti Computing.</div></div></div></footer></div></body></html>"
